{IfUpgraded:show:Gain {HungerPower:diff()} [gold]Hunger[/gold].
}Gain {Block:diff()} [gold]Block[/gold] for each [gold]Void[/gold] in your draw pile, then [gold]Exhaust[/gold] ALL of them.
[gold]Block[/gold] is not removed at the start of your next turn.

SPACEMERCS-GLACIAL_GUARD.description:
Gain {Block:diff()} [gold]Block[/gold].
Whenever you're attacked this turn while you have [gold]Block[/gold], apply {GlacialGuardPower:diff()} [color=cyan]Slowed[/color] to the enemy.{IfUpgraded:show:
